WEBVTT

01:39.390 --> 01:43.090
[Road to Success]

01:44.950 --> 01:47.890
[Episode 26]

01:48.000 --> 01:48.870
-Come on, eat up.
-It's ready.

01:48.870 --> 01:49.680
-Slow down.
-Guys,

01:49.680 --> 01:52.120
Lin Lu and Zheng Feiyang's barbecue
is here!

01:52.120 --> 01:54.320
-Finally!
-Smells so good!

01:54.350 --> 01:56.610
-Finally done.
-How do we roast the corn?

01:58.950 --> 02:00.590
There's no occasion

02:01.000 --> 02:03.000
a hot pot can't celebrate.

02:03.020 --> 02:05.180
If there is, throw a barbecue too.

02:05.280 --> 02:07.280
And if the occasion's big enough,

02:07.280 --> 02:08.400
have both.

02:09.280 --> 02:09.910
So,

02:10.190 --> 02:11.960
to celebrate our team,
Hongjing No. 8 High,

02:11.960 --> 02:14.030
beating 2 professional league youth teams

02:14.030 --> 02:15.280
and advancing from

02:15.280 --> 02:17.120
the group stage
in second place with 6 points,

02:17.120 --> 02:18.360
let's raise a glass!

02:18.390 --> 02:19.370
Come on, come on!

02:19.400 --> 02:20.200
Come on!

02:20.230 --> 02:23.000
-Cheers!
-Come on, cheers!

02:23.079 --> 02:24.000
Thank you, Coach!

02:24.000 --> 02:25.150
Thank you, Coach.

02:25.170 --> 02:27.300
-Thank you, Coach.
-Thank you, Coach.

02:27.470 --> 02:27.910
Eat up.

02:29.030 --> 02:30.340
I'm going to grab some barbecue.

02:30.340 --> 02:31.740
-Throw in some meatballs
-Feng Suo.

02:31.740 --> 02:32.370
No need.

02:35.910 --> 02:37.240
The corn is on the grill.

02:38.280 --> 02:39.430
Want some corn?

02:39.970 --> 02:41.090
Chengye,

02:41.120 --> 02:42.520
how have you been lately?

02:44.079 --> 02:45.000
Give me a chicken wing.

02:45.000 --> 02:47.460
As long as there are matches to play,
I'm good.

02:47.460 --> 02:48.630
Cut it out, you guys!

02:48.680 --> 02:49.630
One skewer each!

02:49.940 --> 02:51.200
How are things at home?

02:51.630 --> 02:52.190
Fine, fine.

02:52.190 --> 02:53.560
One at a time.

02:53.560 --> 02:55.290
Ever since we started winning,

02:55.360 --> 02:57.090
they've stopped complaining.

02:58.710 --> 02:59.310
Thank you.

03:04.430 --> 03:06.030
Actually, I've always felt

03:06.470 --> 03:08.600
you shouldn't be trapped by your past.

03:09.120 --> 03:10.000
Your parents,

03:10.360 --> 03:11.310
your family,

03:11.960 --> 03:14.020
and everything you've been through—

03:14.590 --> 03:15.840
none of that should

03:15.840 --> 03:17.560
define who you'll become.

03:19.470 --> 03:19.930
Then...

03:21.030 --> 03:22.430
then what does define it?

03:22.590 --> 03:23.870
Yourself, of course.

03:25.400 --> 03:26.120
Only you

03:26.870 --> 03:28.430
can define who you are.

03:37.400 --> 03:38.680
Wen Chengye,

03:39.150 --> 03:41.680
it's a disgrace not to help out, you know.

03:44.079 --> 03:46.280
Qin Ao, did you help?

03:46.600 --> 03:47.570
Nope.

03:47.600 --> 03:49.320
So I'm a disgrace.

03:51.560 --> 03:53.650
You're so shameless.

03:55.030 --> 03:56.760
Who are you calling shameless?

03:58.100 --> 04:00.030
Ms. Lin, you've made huge strides

04:00.050 --> 04:01.250
in education lately.

04:02.840 --> 04:03.710
It's alright.

04:04.360 --> 04:07.450
But tonight, the spotlight definitely
belongs to you, Coach Wang.

04:07.450 --> 04:09.040
Come on, let's drink till we drop.

04:09.040 --> 04:10.320
No oysters?

04:10.350 --> 04:11.390
Why are you taking so much?

04:11.390 --> 04:12.990
I'm just grabbing some meat.

04:13.000 --> 04:13.990
I'm not eating that much.

04:13.990 --> 04:14.990
Give him the food.

04:15.590 --> 04:16.560
Ms. Lin,

04:16.560 --> 04:18.269
look at Wen Chengye
making a fool of himself.

04:18.269 --> 04:19.930
You're a bigger fool than I am.

04:21.690 --> 04:24.020
Am I walking okay?

04:25.000 --> 04:27.000
You're walking perfectly fine.

04:29.270 --> 04:30.600
We're here.

04:38.390 --> 04:39.510
Hold on.

04:41.720 --> 04:43.280
I dribble...

04:43.840 --> 04:46.090
Shoot!

04:46.350 --> 04:47.350
You scored?

04:48.270 --> 04:51.070
Don't I have talent for football?

04:51.390 --> 04:52.510
You do.

04:54.310 --> 04:56.180
My feet are so cold.

05:10.510 --> 05:11.840
What? Not feeling well?

05:13.720 --> 05:15.380
I'll go get some water for you.

05:16.600 --> 05:17.830
Wang Fa...

05:18.950 --> 05:21.560
Wang Fa, where are you going?

05:24.750 --> 05:27.070
Wang Fa...

05:45.120 --> 05:48.870
I'm glad you're here, Wang Fa.

05:51.750 --> 05:52.630
Alright.

05:53.000 --> 05:54.070
Rest early.

05:54.659 --> 05:56.560
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

05:57.200 --> 05:59.490
♪ On the summer night ♪

06:00.050 --> 06:05.410
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

06:01.870 --> 06:06.700
Do... Do I have a talent for football?

06:06.830 --> 06:08.070
You do.

06:07.080 --> 06:09.340
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

06:10.050 --> 06:15.840
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

06:19.450 --> 06:24.570
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

06:21.070 --> 06:22.750
Shoot!

06:23.560 --> 06:26.810
I scored... Another goal...

06:25.300 --> 06:30.680
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

06:26.950 --> 06:28.390
Attack!

06:29.950 --> 06:31.630
One more!

06:31.520 --> 06:33.820
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

06:32.000 --> 06:33.720
Shoot!

06:33.830 --> 06:35.870
Take another shot!

06:34.490 --> 06:40.310
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

06:40.070 --> 06:42.190
What's the score now?

06:43.240 --> 06:44.750
Ten to zero.

06:43.550 --> 06:45.380
♪ Every night ♪

06:44.750 --> 06:46.560
Who's got 10?

06:46.300 --> 06:48.270
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

06:46.560 --> 06:48.070
You do. I've got 0.

06:49.170 --> 06:50.960
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

06:49.510 --> 06:50.390
Go to sleep.

06:51.570 --> 06:53.780
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

06:54.950 --> 06:57.530
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

06:58.550 --> 07:00.310
♪ Because of your love ♪

07:01.240 --> 07:05.740
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

07:26.990 --> 07:28.880
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

07:29.510 --> 07:31.800
♪ On the summer night ♪

07:32.380 --> 07:37.730
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

07:39.400 --> 07:41.659
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

07:42.370 --> 07:48.159
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

08:28.010 --> 08:29.550
Why is my room so clean?

09:37.340 --> 09:39.770
Did you turn into
a little house elf, Coach?

09:37.500 --> 09:40.770
[Winfred]

09:41.920 --> 09:42.920
You're up.

10:01.240 --> 10:03.240
Where's my facial cleansing brush?

10:09.960 --> 10:13.210
[Winfred]

10:10.480 --> 10:12.480
Where's my facial cleansing brush?

10:16.380 --> 10:17.740
What brush?

10:19.320 --> 10:21.250
The one I left on the bathroom sink.

10:21.520 --> 10:22.800
I know which one.

10:22.830 --> 10:25.210
But are you sure you still want it?

10:34.870 --> 10:37.200
Looking for your facial cleansing brush?

10:50.320 --> 10:51.840
Why is it here?

11:02.720 --> 11:05.180
This isn't meant for
cleaning shoes, right?

11:05.480 --> 11:07.680
What would a clueless guy like you know?

11:07.910 --> 11:11.550
It's whatever kind of brush I say it is.

11:21.240 --> 11:23.000
Why didn't you stop me?

11:23.020 --> 11:25.050
You insisted on
cleaning your shoes yourself.

11:25.050 --> 11:26.180
I couldn't stop you.

11:27.000 --> 11:29.520
I'll have to buy another one.

11:29.550 --> 11:30.440
Don't worry.

11:30.440 --> 11:32.200
I've ordered the latest model for you.

11:32.200 --> 11:33.200
Make sure you get it when it arrives.

11:33.200 --> 11:34.320
Really?

11:34.320 --> 11:35.550
That's so sweet.

11:39.480 --> 11:40.240
I'm hungry.

11:40.240 --> 11:41.870
Let's go to your place for a healthy meal.

11:41.870 --> 11:43.240
We'll eat at your place today.

11:43.240 --> 11:44.240
I'll cook for you.

11:45.790 --> 11:46.920
You know how to cook?

11:56.840 --> 11:59.150
You're making fried noodles for me?

11:59.150 --> 12:01.000
Let me show you the superb cooking skills

12:01.000 --> 12:02.240
of a UK returnee.

12:04.600 --> 12:06.320
Then I'm looking forward to it.

12:06.320 --> 12:07.910
I'm going to wash up.

12:23.200 --> 12:24.960
It looks quite good.

12:25.670 --> 12:26.440
Go on, try it.

12:37.960 --> 12:40.200
It tastes even better than it looks.

12:41.550 --> 12:43.150
Really? Then have some more.

12:59.630 --> 13:00.690
I'm full and happy.

13:02.240 --> 13:03.670
Since Coach House-Elf

13:03.670 --> 13:05.470
showed off his amazing cooking,

13:05.670 --> 13:07.000
I must return the favor.

13:09.570 --> 13:10.810
Close your eyes.

13:34.600 --> 13:37.200
From now on, if you want to come over,

13:37.200 --> 13:38.720
you don't need to knock.

13:38.720 --> 13:40.320
Just use the key.

13:43.320 --> 13:45.030
You always hide the key

13:45.030 --> 13:46.550
under the shoe cabinet.

13:47.390 --> 13:49.080
I can get in without knocking anyway.

13:49.080 --> 13:50.200
You knew that?

13:55.360 --> 13:57.960
Thank you, Ms. Lin,
for formally accepting me.

14:02.810 --> 14:04.160
Parachute drop, follow me.

14:02.910 --> 14:05.510
[Fishing Village]

14:04.390 --> 14:05.670
Stick with me.

14:05.670 --> 14:07.750
Enemy, southwest, 450 degrees!

14:07.750 --> 14:09.600
There are too many of them. I'm hiding.

14:09.600 --> 14:11.480
-I…
-Shoot, shoot!

14:17.840 --> 14:18.960
It's all on you now.

14:19.550 --> 14:20.650
Leave it to me...

14:23.600 --> 14:25.480
Gotta say, that meal of yours

14:25.480 --> 14:27.140
really worked up my appetite.

14:27.790 --> 14:29.670
For dinner...

14:30.320 --> 14:32.430
For dinner, let's have some pan-fried buns
from Granny Wu's.

14:32.430 --> 14:33.910
It's only 4:30 PM now.

14:34.440 --> 14:36.440
People start lining up there by 5 PM.

14:37.080 --> 14:38.200
I'm dead too.

14:44.130 --> 14:46.640
[Ms. Lin Wanxing,
please come to the school immediately.]

14:46.910 --> 14:48.480
The principal wants to see me.

14:48.480 --> 14:50.870
It's the weekend. What could he want?

14:52.440 --> 14:53.150
Go ahead.

14:53.550 --> 14:55.030
Don't worry about the pan-fried buns.

14:55.030 --> 14:56.290
I'll go line up for you.

14:57.280 --> 14:58.760
I'll leave it to you then.

15:24.540 --> 15:28.260
[Superstar Slacker]

15:24.960 --> 15:26.790
Ms. Lin's gone hunting.

15:26.790 --> 15:27.860
Wait for me to come back.

15:27.860 --> 15:29.230
We'll eat the pan-fried buns together.

15:29.230 --> 15:30.230
Bye.

15:30.840 --> 15:31.440
Bye.

15:44.270 --> 15:47.170
[Administrative Building]

15:46.320 --> 15:47.150
Come in.

15:47.840 --> 15:49.640
Principal, you wanted to see me?

15:49.840 --> 15:50.720
Ms. Lin.

15:51.840 --> 15:52.670
Sit.

16:03.150 --> 16:04.350
I asked you here today

16:04.840 --> 16:06.370
because there's something

16:06.960 --> 16:08.550
I need to verify with you.

16:26.240 --> 16:27.360
Ms. Lin.

16:28.200 --> 16:31.660
Your boyfriend's been waiting for you there
for quite a while.

16:41.790 --> 16:43.320
Have you been waiting long?

16:56.440 --> 16:58.240
I bought you the pan-fried buns.

16:58.340 --> 16:59.480
Why did it take so long?

16:59.480 --> 17:00.530
They're cold now.

17:01.200 --> 17:02.550
You actually got them.

17:03.380 --> 17:04.230
Let's go.

17:06.240 --> 17:08.240
Did the principal ask you anything?

17:10.069 --> 17:11.920
He just asked a few things
about the team's

17:11.920 --> 17:13.920
next stage now that we've advanced.

17:15.599 --> 17:16.619
He's that eager?

17:17.030 --> 17:19.290
Calling you in on a weekend just for that.

17:21.500 --> 17:23.030
Building a stronger sporting nation.

17:23.030 --> 17:25.960
What's wrong with
caring about the next generation?

17:28.440 --> 17:30.550
What's the filling in these?

17:32.070 --> 17:32.920
They're cold now.

17:32.920 --> 17:33.980
Don't eat them yet.

17:34.030 --> 17:35.960
Let's heat them up when we get back.

17:36.480 --> 17:37.110
Okay.

18:00.240 --> 18:01.770
I've got a bit of a headache.

18:01.830 --> 18:03.000
I want to rest first.

18:03.200 --> 18:04.600
Why the sudden headache?

18:05.030 --> 18:07.090
Maybe I didn't sleep well last night.

18:07.200 --> 18:08.660
But you haven't eaten yet.

18:10.160 --> 18:11.820
Aren't there pan-fried buns?

18:15.550 --> 18:17.550
Remember to heat them up in the oven.

18:22.830 --> 18:23.720
Lin Wanxing.

18:25.350 --> 18:26.480
Are you really okay?

18:28.160 --> 18:29.050
I'm fine.

18:29.720 --> 18:31.400
I'm just a little tired.

18:45.440 --> 18:47.680
Don't worry, Coach House-Elf.

18:53.190 --> 18:54.190
See you tomorrow.

18:55.200 --> 18:56.350
See you tomorrow.

19:24.110 --> 19:25.220
Someone has reported

19:25.220 --> 19:28.910
[Report Letter]

19:25.880 --> 19:27.440
that you were expelled

19:27.720 --> 19:30.780
from Yongchuan University
for some unsavory reasons.

19:31.240 --> 19:32.110
Ms. Lin,

19:32.880 --> 19:34.540
the school trusts you deeply.

19:35.560 --> 19:38.020
We hope you'll handle
this matter properly.

20:04.490 --> 20:09.450
[Over a year ago]

20:06.490 --> 20:07.440
Professor Shu?

20:08.410 --> 20:09.560
Professor Shu!

20:09.590 --> 20:10.550
Save him!

20:10.550 --> 20:11.620
Professor Shu!

20:11.650 --> 20:13.510
-Professor Shu!
-Professor Shu!

20:14.000 --> 20:15.400
Call an ambulance!

20:15.400 --> 20:16.350
Hello?

20:16.410 --> 20:19.590
[Goodbye, My Love]

20:20.720 --> 20:22.200
Is that Lin Wanxing?

20:22.200 --> 20:24.590
The one who seduced a professor
and knowingly became the other woman?

20:24.590 --> 20:25.440
Yeah.

20:25.440 --> 20:27.000
Professor Shu was a good man.

20:27.000 --> 20:28.880
I even took his class.

20:29.450 --> 20:30.900
[Withdrawal Application]

20:29.590 --> 20:31.200
If you apply to withdraw from school now,

20:31.200 --> 20:32.790
you can still preserve
what little dignity is left

20:32.790 --> 20:34.310
for yourself and Professor Shu.

20:34.310 --> 20:35.440
Mom,

20:35.440 --> 20:36.880
even you don't believe me?

20:36.880 --> 20:37.920
Sign it.

20:40.000 --> 20:40.960
Grandpa...

20:42.790 --> 20:43.920
passed away.

20:44.720 --> 20:46.030
That's impossible.

20:46.030 --> 20:47.160
Where is Grandpa?

20:47.160 --> 20:48.200
I want to see him!

20:48.200 --> 20:50.160
He's already been cremated.

20:52.480 --> 20:53.750
What?

20:56.920 --> 20:58.680
Why didn't you tell me?

20:59.570 --> 21:01.630
Why didn't you tell me?

21:03.030 --> 21:04.160
Where are you going?

21:09.730 --> 21:12.590
Wanxing, isn't it inappropriate for you
to be here?

21:14.720 --> 21:15.550
Shuyun,

21:16.350 --> 21:17.830
what do you mean by that?

21:18.400 --> 21:19.200
Aunt,

21:19.680 --> 21:22.160
you and Uncle devoted
your whole lives to teaching

21:22.160 --> 21:23.960
and earned everyone's respect.

21:24.640 --> 21:26.720
But Wanxing is a disappointment

21:26.720 --> 21:28.210
and has let you down.

21:28.240 --> 21:30.350
If you ask me,
she never should've come back.

21:30.350 --> 21:32.830
Alright, you've offered the incense.

21:32.830 --> 21:33.880
You can leave now.

21:33.880 --> 21:37.040
Aunt, I'm only thinking of you.

21:37.060 --> 21:39.020
When Uncle was gravely ill,

21:39.070 --> 21:41.750
she was out there
doing those shameful things,

21:41.750 --> 21:43.000
making you both suffer!

21:43.000 --> 21:44.110
If it hadn't been for her,

21:44.110 --> 21:45.970
Uncle wouldn't have passed away!

21:47.640 --> 21:48.550
Aunt Shuyun.

21:51.400 --> 21:52.750
Those were just rumors.

21:52.750 --> 21:53.720
Rumors?

21:53.720 --> 21:55.510
There's no smoke without fire.

21:55.510 --> 21:56.920
Why pick on you and not the others?

21:56.920 --> 21:58.350
I believe Wanxing!

21:58.350 --> 22:00.440
I won't let you insult her!

22:00.440 --> 22:02.000
I insult her?

22:02.440 --> 22:05.070
She still hasn't reflected on herself
to this day.

22:05.070 --> 22:06.640
Do you know what everyone's been

22:06.640 --> 22:08.310
saying about her in the family?

22:08.310 --> 22:09.830
She's just brought shame to you!

22:09.830 --> 22:11.640
-To our whole family!
-Enough!

22:11.640 --> 22:12.350
Shut up!

22:12.350 --> 22:13.510
Me? Shut up?

22:13.510 --> 22:15.880
Aunt, you threw my kindness
back in my face!

22:15.880 --> 22:17.270
-You really...
-Get out!

22:17.270 --> 22:18.590
You can get out now!

22:20.880 --> 22:23.010
-Me?
-She's the one who should get out!

22:25.440 --> 22:27.770
-Grandma! Grandma!
-Grandma!

22:27.790 --> 22:33.120
-Grandma! Grandma!
-Grandma!

22:34.970 --> 22:36.100
Grandma,

22:36.750 --> 22:38.220
it's all my fault.

22:38.460 --> 22:40.740
If it hadn't been for me,

22:41.200 --> 22:43.060
you wouldn't have been like this.

23:13.260 --> 23:16.880
[Superstar Slacker]

23:13.630 --> 23:16.040
How are you? Does your head still hurt?

23:21.270 --> 23:24.400
I'm okay. I took some medicine,
and I'm going to sleep.

23:33.410 --> 23:37.740
[Superstar Slacker]

23:34.790 --> 23:36.970
Good night. See you tomorrow.

24:04.920 --> 24:07.030
Lin Wanxing, it's 7:30.

24:07.030 --> 24:08.110
Time to get up.

24:09.510 --> 24:11.240
I bought you rice noodle rolls.

24:14.750 --> 24:15.680
Wanxing?

24:32.400 --> 24:33.200
Wanxing.

24:36.880 --> 24:38.280
We're going to be late...

24:44.270 --> 24:45.270
Lin Wanxing!

24:47.060 --> 24:47.940
[I'm sorry. I've already left.]

24:52.400 --> 24:55.560
I'm sorry. I've already left.

25:11.830 --> 25:12.640
Wanxing!

25:13.880 --> 25:15.110
Lin Wanxing!

25:22.920 --> 25:23.920
Where is Wanxing?

25:26.350 --> 25:27.830
Her phone's off.

25:29.830 --> 25:31.590
She sent me this WeChat message
early this morning.

25:31.590 --> 25:33.200
I called her right after seeing it,

25:33.200 --> 25:34.700
but I couldn't get through.

25:34.700 --> 25:36.070
[Li, I've left.
I'll leave the team to you.]

25:36.090 --> 25:36.840
[All the materials
are on my coffee table.]

25:37.110 --> 25:38.710
Did something happen to her?

25:39.350 --> 25:42.160
The principal spoke with her
for a long time yesterday.

25:42.160 --> 25:44.360
She wasn't herself after she came back.

25:47.680 --> 25:48.510
In the end...

25:50.350 --> 25:51.830
it happened after all.

25:52.680 --> 25:53.510
No,

25:53.750 --> 25:54.880
I have to go find her.

25:55.310 --> 25:57.750
Are you just going to run around
looking for her like a headless chicken?

25:57.750 --> 25:58.800
Tell me first,

25:59.830 --> 26:01.070
what happened?

26:10.240 --> 26:11.030
I had no idea

26:12.960 --> 26:14.750
she'd been through all that.

26:18.240 --> 26:19.900
I don't believe those rumors.

26:21.350 --> 26:23.350
But what difference does it make?

26:24.070 --> 26:25.350
Plenty of people do.

26:27.820 --> 26:30.080
After Wanxing dropped out of Yongchuan,

26:31.880 --> 26:34.210
she went through a really difficult time.

26:37.470 --> 26:39.140
Actually, ever since she was little,

26:39.140 --> 26:41.540
she's always been
a very, very strong girl.

26:43.110 --> 26:44.590
I remember...

26:45.270 --> 26:46.630
back in middle school,

26:46.830 --> 26:49.790
a chubby kid in our class
falsely accused her of stealing his pen.

26:49.790 --> 26:51.790
She chased after him and beat him up.

26:52.110 --> 26:53.770
She even grabbed his backpack

26:54.110 --> 26:55.640
until she found

26:55.640 --> 26:57.550
the pen inside.

27:01.310 --> 27:03.040
I still remember

27:03.400 --> 27:05.000
her holding up that pen

27:06.440 --> 27:09.370
and splattering ink all over him.
She looked so cool.

27:10.550 --> 27:12.880
But not every situation gives a person...

27:14.310 --> 27:16.370
the chance to prove their innocence.

27:20.790 --> 27:23.200
You came back to Hongjing
after learning about

27:23.200 --> 27:24.620
all that, didn't you?

27:30.200 --> 27:32.000
After we went our separate ways,

27:33.070 --> 27:34.800
I always kept a close eye on her.

27:35.440 --> 27:38.300
I often checked her
various social media accounts.

27:38.590 --> 27:41.110
At some point, I noticed
she'd suddenly disappeared.

27:41.110 --> 27:43.000
So I called people at Yongchuan

27:43.440 --> 27:45.000
to ask about her.

27:46.200 --> 27:48.030
That was when I found out

27:48.680 --> 27:50.210
she'd gotten into trouble.

27:52.270 --> 27:54.110
In front of her, I always pretended

27:54.110 --> 27:55.590
I didn't know anything.

27:59.680 --> 28:00.550
I thought...

28:02.590 --> 28:04.650
I could be there for her if I came back.

28:06.750 --> 28:08.880
If she really couldn't get through it,

28:09.200 --> 28:11.460
I'd take her back to Switzerland with me.

28:14.480 --> 28:16.410
I thought she'd finally healed...

28:19.000 --> 28:21.130
and that she'd found the right man too.

28:29.920 --> 28:31.350
I failed to protect her.

28:38.090 --> 28:40.940
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team
Training Unit Plan]

28:42.590 --> 28:44.270
That's all I know.

28:46.270 --> 28:48.590
No matter what,
I still have to go find her.

28:48.590 --> 28:50.050
Even if I can't find her...

28:51.510 --> 28:53.640
I'll do my best to hold the fort for her.

29:06.880 --> 29:07.730
Li,

29:07.760 --> 29:09.240
I've left.

29:10.310 --> 29:12.060
I'll leave the team to you.

29:12.410 --> 29:14.750
All the materials are on my coffee table.

29:24.400 --> 29:25.680
He's a light sleeper,

29:25.680 --> 29:27.680
so I can't send him a WeChat message.

29:35.830 --> 29:37.020
I'm sorry.

29:37.400 --> 29:38.810
I've already left.

29:48.540 --> 29:50.290
[I'm sorry. I've already left.]

31:01.690 --> 31:03.730
[Knowledge is Boundless]

31:03.070 --> 31:03.810
"Xiju." (Comedy)

31:03.810 --> 31:04.480
Comedy.

31:04.480 --> 31:05.370
How to spell it?

31:05.400 --> 31:08.310
C-o-m-e-d-y.

31:08.310 --> 31:09.200
Okay.

31:09.590 --> 31:10.590
"Kouyin." (Accent)

31:10.590 --> 31:11.790
Accent.

31:11.790 --> 31:12.990
Okay, how to spell it?

31:13.680 --> 31:14.310
Hey, check the forum.

31:14.310 --> 31:17.070
It's Ms. Lin from
the sports equipment room, right?

31:17.070 --> 31:18.720
Her dirty past has been exposed!

31:18.720 --> 31:20.240
Her dirty past has been exposed.

31:20.080 --> 31:20.730
[Lin Wanxing, Sports Equipment Room Teacher:
Morally Corrupt,]

31:20.240 --> 31:22.440
Knowingly the other woman,
and responsible for a professor's death?

31:20.750 --> 31:21.680
[Knowingly the Other Woman,
Responsible for a Professor's Death,]

31:24.200 --> 31:25.640
-What?
-What the hell is this?

31:25.320 --> 31:25.940
[Lin Wanxing, Sports Equipment Room Teacher:
Morally Corrupt,]

31:25.640 --> 31:27.030
Turn it off! Turn it off!

31:25.960 --> 31:26.330
[Knowingly the Other Woman,
Responsible for a Professor's Death,]

31:26.330 --> 31:26.700
[Expelled from Yongchuan University!]

31:27.830 --> 31:28.550
Let's go find Ms. Lin.

31:28.550 --> 31:29.550
Let's go. Come on.

31:29.750 --> 31:30.830
Is it real?

31:30.830 --> 31:31.880
Turn that off!

31:34.070 --> 31:35.240
I didn't see her.

31:35.440 --> 31:36.240
Is she over here?

31:36.240 --> 31:36.830
Not in here.

31:36.830 --> 31:38.030
Not over here either.

31:38.750 --> 31:40.330
[Sports Equipment Room]

31:38.830 --> 31:39.960
Is Ms. Lin not here?

31:40.480 --> 31:42.110
You saw the forum too, right?

31:43.480 --> 31:45.790
I'm not sure
whether Ms. Lin has seen it yet.

31:45.790 --> 31:47.000
Let's hope she hasn't.

31:47.000 --> 31:48.290
How could she not?

31:48.350 --> 31:49.830
I don't know where she went.

31:49.830 --> 31:51.550
Text Ms. Lin on your phone.

31:51.550 --> 31:52.720
Let's just go find her directly.

31:52.720 --> 31:54.050
Do you know where she is?

31:54.830 --> 31:56.270
Everyone, let's go back to class first.

31:56.270 --> 31:59.130
We'll figure something out together
after school.

32:00.640 --> 32:01.170
Let's go.

32:07.810 --> 32:08.360
[Good thing I'm not on the football team.
I don't have to face this.]

32:08.380 --> 32:08.930
[She's quite a piece of work.
So who's she after]

32:08.960 --> 32:09.930
[at our school? Old Demon Jin and Qian
don't have anything worth taking, anyway.]

32:09.960 --> 32:10.890
[Disgusting.
Apparently, anyone can be a teacher now.]

32:10.920 --> 32:11.810
[If this gets out,]

32:11.830 --> 32:12.340
[we'll never be able to hold our heads up
when dealing with other schools.]

32:12.370 --> 32:12.750
[Let's all sign a petition
to drive Lin Wanxing out.]

32:12.780 --> 32:13.610
[The problem now is not who hired her.]

32:13.640 --> 32:14.630
[The real question is what the school
will do with her—fire her or keep her?]

32:14.650 --> 32:15.190
[The thread title
sounds kind of personal.]

32:15.220 --> 32:15.800
[Maybe the OP got rejected by her.]

32:15.820 --> 32:16.820
[Otherwise, why be so obsessed
with a teacher from the equipment room?]

32:31.080 --> 32:32.890
When I was 8 years old,

32:32.970 --> 32:34.500
my dad also wronged me once.

32:35.270 --> 32:36.870
The things he said to scold me

32:36.920 --> 32:37.680
haunted me

32:37.680 --> 32:39.550
for quite a while.

32:40.590 --> 32:42.960
So much so that even after I grew up,

32:43.640 --> 32:45.040
whenever I hit a setback,

32:45.680 --> 32:47.720
thinking of what he'd said back then

32:48.790 --> 32:51.450
would shatter my courage
to face difficulties.

32:53.360 --> 32:54.860
It wasn't me.

32:55.640 --> 32:57.590
I didn't do those things.

32:57.590 --> 32:58.890
I didn't do it.

33:00.680 --> 33:01.880
A few months ago,

33:03.200 --> 33:04.730
I was in a really bad state.

33:07.050 --> 33:09.010
I also stood at the edge
of a very high place.

33:07.900 --> 33:09.610
[Let's end it then.
I don't want to see you again.]

33:09.630 --> 33:10.380
[Start from the highest point.]

33:10.070 --> 33:11.550
I thought...

33:10.400 --> 33:10.970
[At least I can hold onto the feeling
of flying for a few seconds.]

33:12.590 --> 33:14.310
if I just jumped,

33:14.880 --> 33:16.590
I'd finally be free.

33:20.270 --> 33:21.590
So

33:22.440 --> 33:24.720
this is what she'd been through—

33:26.170 --> 33:29.310
slandered, expelled,

33:29.640 --> 33:31.290
and locked up by her parents.

33:32.070 --> 33:34.670
She couldn't even
see her beloved grandfather

33:34.720 --> 33:36.000
for the last time.

33:37.510 --> 33:40.920
Yet she still put up a strong front

33:41.200 --> 33:42.830
and chose to stay.

33:43.680 --> 33:45.640
But Wang Fa, what did you do?

33:46.000 --> 33:47.700
You doubted her

33:47.920 --> 33:49.240
and investigated her.

33:50.030 --> 33:51.310
You tore open her deepest wound—

33:51.310 --> 33:53.310
the wound of not being trusted.

33:53.650 --> 33:54.770
Wang Fa,

33:55.110 --> 33:57.840
how could you
possibly deserve her forgiveness?

33:59.240 --> 34:00.680
Lin Wanxing,

34:00.910 --> 34:02.740
no matter where you've gone,

34:03.010 --> 34:04.570
I will find you,

34:05.240 --> 34:06.900
and I'll be there to catch you.

34:09.110 --> 34:11.290
Fu, are you stupid or what?

34:11.510 --> 34:13.030
That bastard was badmouthing Ms. Lin,

34:13.030 --> 34:14.360
and you went after him all by yourself?

34:14.360 --> 34:15.070
Did you have no one backing you up?

34:15.070 --> 34:16.710
Or did we all die or something?

34:16.710 --> 34:19.400
Yeah! Next time
something like this happens, tell us.

34:19.400 --> 34:21.800
You have to tell us
when something happens.

34:21.840 --> 34:23.190
Okay, I know.

34:23.190 --> 34:25.070
Do you think Ms. Lin will come back today?

34:25.070 --> 34:26.550
How would I know?

34:26.670 --> 34:27.550
Hard to say.

34:27.880 --> 34:28.630
I don't know.

34:29.840 --> 34:30.790
Hello, Ms. Ju.

34:30.820 --> 34:31.420
Hello, Ms. Ju.

34:31.420 --> 34:32.630
Hello, Ms. Ju.

34:37.550 --> 34:38.360
Everyone,

34:39.320 --> 34:40.400
starting today,

34:40.630 --> 34:42.290
I'm your new team supervisor.

34:43.510 --> 34:45.400
Wait, how did you become our supervisor?

34:45.400 --> 34:47.030
Our supervisor is Ms. Lin.

34:47.030 --> 34:48.800
Yeah, it can only be Ms. Lin.

34:50.239 --> 34:51.989
Ms. Lin...

34:52.400 --> 34:53.840
has to step away for a while.

34:53.840 --> 34:54.590
Without Ms. Lin,

34:54.590 --> 34:55.880
what's the point of playing football?

34:55.880 --> 34:57.190
Yeah, without Ms. Lin,

34:57.190 --> 34:58.550
this team would have been
disbanded long ago.

34:58.550 --> 35:01.750
The team's heart isn't here.
What are we even playing for?

35:03.070 --> 35:04.640
Do you all trust Ms. Lin?

35:04.670 --> 35:05.400
Of course.

35:05.400 --> 35:07.130
That doesn't even need asking!

35:09.510 --> 35:11.040
Then, do you still remember

35:11.290 --> 35:14.090
the answer you handed in
for Ms. Lin's assignment?

35:18.990 --> 35:21.100
[We]

35:26.320 --> 35:31.680
[We play football to win]

35:32.360 --> 35:34.090
This is the answer you gave her.

35:38.740 --> 35:40.700
But if you give up football now,

35:41.630 --> 35:42.840
then when I bring Ms. Lin back,

35:42.840 --> 35:43.840
will you still be able to tell her

35:43.840 --> 35:45.500
that you play football to win?

35:52.400 --> 35:53.400
Coach,

35:53.770 --> 35:55.640
can you really bring Ms. Lin back?

35:56.800 --> 35:57.440
I can.

36:01.240 --> 36:02.640
But will you be able to

36:02.660 --> 36:04.460
welcome her back with a victory?

36:10.510 --> 36:13.860
[We play football to win]

36:16.360 --> 36:17.150
Okay.

36:18.110 --> 36:19.550
I've reviewed the materials.

36:19.550 --> 36:22.110
Our next match is in 2 weeks.

36:56.070 --> 36:58.190
Wang Fa, I'm still looking for her.

36:57.830 --> 36:59.950
[Wang Tian]

36:58.190 --> 36:59.550
Wait for my news.

37:18.480 --> 37:19.630
You're really something.

37:19.630 --> 37:21.400
You came all the way here,
but you wouldn't come up to my office.

37:21.400 --> 37:23.660
And I had to come down
to see you personally.

37:23.660 --> 37:26.280
Tian, did you find anything?

37:30.280 --> 37:31.280
Seeing you like this,

37:31.280 --> 37:33.210
I don't even feel like teasing you.

37:37.070 --> 37:38.660
She was spotted in Hanling,

37:38.760 --> 37:41.160
but I didn't track down
her exact location.

37:42.810 --> 37:44.000
Hanling...

37:54.440 --> 37:55.800
Sitting around
at a dog café waiting like this

37:55.800 --> 37:57.320
is really dumb, you know.

37:57.320 --> 37:58.440
Hanling is huge.

37:58.440 --> 38:00.110
There are tons of dog cafés.

38:00.110 --> 38:01.910
Then I'll search them one by one.

38:02.440 --> 38:04.880
You'd be better off
letting me hire a private investigator.

38:04.880 --> 38:05.760
No.

38:05.760 --> 38:08.290
She probably just wants to
be alone right now.

38:09.190 --> 38:10.630
Then why are you here?

38:13.030 --> 38:14.690
She can choose not to see me...

38:15.800 --> 38:17.400
but I have to be there for her.

38:19.320 --> 38:20.230
I get it.

38:20.230 --> 38:22.280
You're doing that whole
"moved by your own devotion" thing.

38:22.280 --> 38:23.880
I'm right here with you, bro.

38:25.960 --> 38:27.000
Take that off.

38:28.630 --> 38:29.320
They don't want to wear it,

38:29.320 --> 38:30.670
so someone has to.

38:31.110 --> 38:32.320
You're back.

38:32.320 --> 38:34.670
Let me put it on you.

38:36.750 --> 38:38.740
♪ Our words flow ♪

38:39.480 --> 38:41.280
No. One more. Is that enough?

38:40.220 --> 38:42.220
♪ A gentle stream ♪

38:41.280 --> 38:43.110
Yeah, that's enough.

38:44.530 --> 38:46.710
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

38:47.360 --> 38:49.880
♪ Inside a silken dream ♪

38:52.090 --> 38:58.000
♪ We talk the cool night, breeze away ♪

38:59.920 --> 39:01.420
♪ We trace the roads ♪

39:02.320 --> 39:05.250
♪ That never see an end ♪

39:08.110 --> 39:11.340
♪ We softly calm the hidden doubt ♪

39:09.960 --> 39:12.920
Our quarterfinal opponent
this time will be

39:11.270 --> 39:15.770
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]
[Quarterfinals]

39:12.310 --> 39:16.790
♪ Seen in each other's eyes ♪

39:12.920 --> 39:14.000
Hanling Victory.

39:14.630 --> 39:16.670
Coach Wang Fa prepared these for you.

39:16.670 --> 39:17.580
Pass them around.

39:17.580 --> 39:21.550
♪ And wake the warmth inside ♪

39:22.360 --> 39:25.250
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]
[Quarterfinals]

39:23.500 --> 39:25.830
♪ Life begins alone ♪

39:26.610 --> 39:29.370
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

39:31.420 --> 39:33.570
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

39:34.240 --> 39:37.510
♪ To light our way back home ♪

39:39.790 --> 39:41.340
♪ True love is not just ♪

39:42.250 --> 39:43.850
♪ The gaze when two hearts first meet ♪

39:44.760 --> 39:49.650
♪ It's courage in the arms ♪

39:51.570 --> 39:54.890
♪ We stand as one ♪

39:54.150 --> 39:55.310
[Hongjing No. 8 High 2–0 Hanling Victory]

39:55.440 --> 39:56.030
Here!

40:03.480 --> 40:09.910
♪And all ♪

40:11.760 --> 40:12.760
-Not bad!
-Yeah!

40:12.780 --> 40:13.590
Nice!

40:14.360 --> 40:15.150
Great shot!

40:22.480 --> 40:23.280
Nice!

40:25.590 --> 40:27.400
Nice shot! Keep it up!

40:29.080 --> 40:33.420
[Hongjing No. 8 High 6–0 Hanling Victory]

41:08.800 --> 41:11.030
We beat Hanling Victory, you know that?

41:16.570 --> 41:22.410
[Little Savage Tribe]

41:17.230 --> 41:19.140
Qin was the MVP.

41:19.190 --> 41:21.150
Qin was unstoppable today.

41:21.150 --> 41:23.110
Wen Chengye was incredible too!

41:24.440 --> 41:27.440
I really wish you could've seen
how awesome we were.

41:24.460 --> 41:27.180
[Little Savage Tribe]

41:29.430 --> 41:33.660
[Little Savage Tribe]

41:30.590 --> 41:33.840
Ms. Lin, are you watching this?

41:45.920 --> 41:47.400
I can vouch for them.

41:47.400 --> 41:49.670
They're not exaggerating at all.

41:59.910 --> 42:02.150
[I can vouch for them.
They're not exaggerating at all.]

42:09.150 --> 42:10.710
When is

42:11.600 --> 42:13.180
Ms. Lin coming back?

42:45.140 --> 42:45.840
[Superstar Slacker]

42:50.770 --> 42:57.000
[Superstar Slacker]

42:51.400 --> 42:52.480
Wanxing,

42:53.190 --> 42:54.670
no matter what happens,

42:54.700 --> 42:56.290
I'm here for you.

43:50.180 --> 43:57.140
[Superstar Slacker]

43:50.630 --> 43:52.120
Those little rascals said

43:52.400 --> 43:55.530
they're saving the victory banquet
until you come back.

44:06.510 --> 44:07.840
We really miss you.

44:08.320 --> 44:09.000
Good night.
